title: Australian diary. No. 091
creator_credit: Australian National Film Board and Jack S. Allan
brief_description: The aeroplane is playing an important part in the Australian economy by transporting perishable goods and general supplies across the vast distances of the continent; grasshoppers are fighting a losing battle against the modern insecticide and the aeroplane; swamplands surrounding Pedbank Weir are attracting migratory birds in their thousands.
